WEBVTT

00:00:59.276 --> 00:01:02.007
who has heard stories
from Uttaranchal to Afghanistan,

00:01:02.031 --> 00:01:04.527
from refugees to officers,

00:01:04.551 --> 00:01:07.247
from children to the elderly.

00:01:07.271 --> 00:01:11.247
He took life-lessons
from one place to another

00:01:11.271 --> 00:01:14.607
and became a source of joy to many.

00:01:14.631 --> 00:01:20.511
Welcome writer, storyteller, life-lesson 
teacher, Deepak Ramola from Dehradun.

00:01:20.539 --> 00:01:26.099
(Applause)